After enabling the high-performance mode, the beauty filter uses less system CPU/GPU resources, which can reduce the heating and lagging of the phone, making it more suitable for long-term use on low-end devices.
 However, please note that after enabling the high-performance mode, the following beauty filter options will not be available:
 1.Eye: Eye width, Eye height, Eye bags
 2.Eyebrow: Eyebrow angle, Eyebrow distance, Eyebrow Height, Eyebrow Length, Eyebrow Thickness, Eyebrow ridge
 3.Mouth: Smile face
 4.Facial: Thin face (Natural, Woman, Man), Slim jaw, Wrinkles, Smile lines. It is recommended to use Face shape to achieve a comprehensive effect of big eyes and thin face
The demo does not support scanning qrcode
